body:
While i was scheming through the season&#039;s resume i fell on jhin&#039;s resume little catch phrase. &quot;Only champion who&#039;s sad about a pentakill.&quot;

It was funny indeed. But that also made me realise something very important..

...HOW IS IT THAT JHIN DOESN&#039;T HAVE A QUADRAKILL VOICE LINE?!
{{sticker:sg-ahri-1}} 
rito pls

replies.body:
Feelsbadman, but as a maker of my own game yeah i can understand the danger of a "rushed champ" , you have no idea if it'll bug and since we're talking about league..

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

Yah. 1% of LoL players having jhin sweet voice would already be insane XD; I can understand it now.

But do you think one day maybe, our dear psychopath will get his quadrakill line? Will the church of the four finally find a voice update in that regard? 

{{sticker:sg-lux}} 

That be amazing.

Don't let yer dreams be dreams. One day maybe, We'll get our quadra kill voiceline.

Still, i would have thought it would be natural for jhin. Even more knowing recent champs all have quadrakill / pentakill voice lines.

{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}
